name: Rebekah
description:
Phone case for iPhone 4/4s OR iPhone 5/5s

*See other designs for a photo of the "snap-on" case structure as this photo of "Rebekah" is displayed on the "protective" case

Hand-printed and assembled
Original artwork

Difference between Snap-on and Protective?
------
Our Snap-on cases are great for those who like to change their cases often. This one is a thin case with rubbery edges that cover all sides of the phone and includes a small lip over the front of the screen. This case does not provide as much protection as our other option, but it's great for a quick change or as an easy gift!

Our Protective cases include a two-piece design: full rubber lining and a tough plastic overcase. There are protective corners and a rubbery lip on the front of the screen. This case provides protection while also being slim and not too bulky.

Both of our case designs are great options! Try both out and see which you prefer.
